snippet.title: Champion Profile: Supergirl
snippet.description:
Supergirl explodes into Infinite Crisis ready and determined to unleash fury and vengeance upon her enemies. Channeling the power of Earth's yellow sun, Supergirl pummels opponents with a relentless stream of attacks befitting her fiery disposition.

Sign up and play Infinite Crisis today! Visit http://www.infinitecrisis.com to start saving the Multiverse!
